      "beat": "setup-1985",
      "order": 1,
      "content": "EXT. HILL VALLEY - DAY (1985)\n\nA skateboard rolls down a suburban sidewalk. MARTY MCFLY (17), in a red vest and Nike high-tops, grabs onto the back of a passing Jeep and rides through the town square of HILL VALLEY.\n\nHe passes the clock tower, its clock frozen at 10:04. A woman hands him a flyer: SAVE THE CLOCK TOWER.\n\nMarty checks his watch and grimaces. Late again.",
