      "beat": "setup-1985",
      "order": 2,
      "content": "INT. MCFLY HOUSE - EVENING\n\nMarty sits at the dinner table across from his parents. GEORGE MCFLY (47) hunches over his plate, laughing nervously at the TV. LORRAINE MCFLY (47) pours another drink.\n\nBIFF TANNEN barges in through the front door, tossing car keys at George.\n\nBIFF: I told you, McFly -- I can't be held responsible if your car isn't up to snuff. Now I need your reports finished by tomorrow morning.\n\nGeorge shrinks in his chair.\n\nGEORGE: Sure, Biff. I'll get right on it.\n\nMarty watches his father submit and looks away, jaw clenching.",
