      "id": "act-1-twin-pines-mall",
      "beat": "the-test",
      "order": 3,
      "content": "EXT. TWIN PINES MALL - PARKING LOT - NIGHT (1:15 AM)\n\nMarty pulls into the empty parking lot on his skateboard. A lone van sits under the sodium lights. DOC BROWN (65), wild-haired and manic, swings open the van doors to reveal --\n\nA DeLorean DMC-12, gleaming under the lights.\n\nDOC: Marty! You made it! Welcome to my latest -- my greatest -- my most spectacular experiment!\n\nDoc gestures grandly at the car. Marty stares.\n\nMARTY: Doc... you built a time machine? Out of a DeLorean?\n\nDoc grins, pointing to a device nestled behind the seats.\n\nDOC: The FLUX CAPACITOR. This is what makes time travel possible.\n\nMarty leans in, squinting at the glowing Y-shaped device.",
