      "id": "act-1-stranded",
      "beat": "stranded-in-1955",
      "order": 4,
      "content": "EXT. PEABODY FARM - NIGHT (1955)\n\nThe DeLorean skids to a halt in a barn, scattering hay and terrifying cattle. Marty stumbles out, coughing.\n\nHe stares at a farmhouse lit by kerosene lamps. No power lines. No TV antennas.\n\nMARTY: This is heavy.\n\nHe runs into town. HILL VALLEY looks completely different -- the courthouse lawn is pristine, the cinema marquee reads CATTLE QUEEN OF MONTANA.\n\nMarty pulls out the fading PHOTOGRAPH of himself and his siblings. His brother's head is starting to disappear.\n\nMARTY (CONT'D): What the hell...?",
